41:03.932 --> 41:08.278
I don't know many people who have kept notes of all these conversations and details.

41:08.338 --> 41:10.922
That's a contradiction.

41:11.443 --> 41:13.526
At least, ostensibly, it's a big contradiction.

41:13.546 --> 41:15.429
But actually, I like both.

