41:32.288 --> 41:34.691
I mean, other people may like it.

41:34.791 --> 41:37.495
I don't put them down, but it's hard to take.

41:37.555 --> 41:38.617
I like surprises.

41:38.637 --> 41:40.820
I meet people that challenge me and so on.

41:41.881 --> 41:42.462
Traveling.

41:43.302 --> 41:47.227
I like it when I don't know what I'm doing.

41:47.287 --> 41:50.552
I think order is on a very rudimentary level.

41:50.572 --> 41:54.257
